  "local_port": 34740,
  "remote_port": 443,
  "prompt": "How can I retrieve my WeChat account if I've forgotten my password, I just linked my linked & I remember I wechat ID.But I don't have QQ/phone linked?",
  "response": "If you've forgotten your WeChat password and don\u2019t have access to a linked phone number or QQ account, you can still try to recover your account using your WeChat ID. Here\u2019s what you can do:\n\n---\n\n### 1. **Use the WeChat ID and Email Address (if linked)**\n   - Open the WeChat app and go to the **Login** screen.\n   - Tap **Forgot Password?** or **More Options** (depending on your app version).\n   - Enter your **WeChat ID** and confirm it.\n   - If you linked an email address to your account, you can request a password reset link to be sent to that email. Follow the instructions in the email to reset your password.\n\n---\n\n### 2. **Contact WeChat Support**\n   - If you don\u2019t have access to a linked email or phone number, you can contact WeChat\u2019s customer support. Here\u2019s how:\n     1. Open the WeChat app and go to the **Login** screen.\n     2. Tap **More Options** or **Help**.\n     3. Look for an option like **Contact Customer Service** or **Account Recovery**.\n     4. Provide your **WeChat ID** and any other details that can help verify your identity (e.g., previous passwords, account history, friends on WeChat, etc.).\n   - WeChat support may ask you to provide additional proof of ownership for the account.\n\n---\n\n### 3. **Use a Friend\u2019s WeChat Account for Verification**\n   - If you have friends on WeChat who can verify your identity, you can ask them to assist with the account recovery process. WeChat may allow you to regain access by verifying your identity through your contacts.\n\n---\n\n### 4. **Create a New Account (if recovery fails)**\n   - If none of the above methods work, you may need to create a new WeChat account. Be sure to link a phone number or email address this time to avoid similar issues in the future.\n\n---\n\n### Tips:\n- Make sure to gather as much information about your account as possible before contacting support (e.g., WeChat ID, approximate registration date, previous devices used, etc.).\n- If you\u2019ve made purchases or have linked bank cards, provide those details to help verify your identity.\n\nGood luck!",
  "temperature": 1.0,
